                  <provenance>The name Tawalda Madḫǝn is written in the
                     supplication formulas throughout the Ms. He is mentioned alone (e.g., <locus target="#6rb">6rb</locus>, 17vb, 22ra) or with other individuals: his father
                     Tasfā Giyorgis (<locus target="#15rb">15rb</locus>, 16vb), his mother Walatta
                     Takla Hāymānot (<locus target="#15rb">15rb</locus>. 16vb) and his wife Walatta
                     Hāymānot (<locus target="#34rb">34rb</locus>, 35va). Another person, gǝrazmač
                     Abrǝha (of) Säsun is mentioned as the buyer in Additio 1.</provenance>
               </history>
